OL,3,CThreat to poison English water supply
OL,4,Cwas feasible, papers show
OL,6,FDetails of a threat to poison English
OL,7,Fwater supplies have emerged in newly
OL,8,Funsealed documents, which show British
OL,9,Fauthorities took the plot seriously as
OL,10,Fit appeared technically feasible.
OL,12,FThe British Embassy and the Papal
OL,13,FNunciature in Dublin received the
OL,14,Fthreat in June 1999 on behalf of what
OL,15,Fwas called the "Republican Revenge
OL,16,FGroup".
