OL,3,CThreat to poison English water supply
OL,4,Cwas feasible, papers show
OL,6,FThe media in London ` including
OL,7,FIreland's national broadcaster RTE and
OL,8,Fthe Irish newspapers ` were called
OL,9,Finto a Government briefing and asked
OL,10,Fnot to report the story, for fear of
OL,11,Fcausing panic over what might well be
OL,12,Fa hoax.
OL,14,FThe Government promised that if a real
OL,15,Fthreat was established, the public
OL,16,Fwould be informed, and said that the
OL,17,Fmedia would be told whether or not
OL,18,Fanything happened when the deadline
OL,19,Fran out.
