OL,6,FMeanwhile in Dublin, gardai were co-
OL,7,Foperating with British police and
OL,8,Fquickly identified a suspect.
OL,10,FThey arrested an ex-soldier from
OL,11,FScotland living in Dublin. He was
OL,12,Fdescribed by some observers as a
OL,13,F"Walter-Mitty character" and he was
OL,14,Fnever charged.
